### Notifications (Admin)

### Get Notifications
GET http://{{host}}/api/notifications
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Create Notification
POST http://{{host}}/api/notifications
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
